  "text": "GANK that are prototypical features among I\u03baB family proteins [CITATION_1] . Importantly, the cycle of induction and suppression of I\u03ba\u0392 causes antipodal oscillations of nuclear NF-\u03baB. The oscillatory pattern induced by this negative-feedback loop may play a functional role in determining the expression pattern of certain NF-\u03baB target genes [CITATION_2] .",
